---
<section
  class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[70vh] px-4 pt-20 pb-12
         text-center text-[#ECF0F1] border-b-4 border-[#3498DB]
         bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2C3E50]/95 to-[#34495E]/95
         bg-[url('/assets/image/ventilation-bg.jpg')] bg-center bg-cover"
>
  <div class="max-w-5xl w-full mx-auto z-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6 text-white drop-shadow-lg">
      Anlita en expert redan idag!
    </h1>
    <p class="text-[#BDC3C7] text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8 font-light leading-relaxed">
      Vi erbjuder professionell service för ditt hem med erfarenhet i hela Sverige.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA Buttons -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-10 py-3 rounded-full 
               text-white font-semibold text-lg md:text-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-[#3498DB] to-[#1ABC9C]
               shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105 transition-all"
      >
        Kontakta oss
      </a>

    
    </div>

